    "description": "Starts Publishing Corporation engages in the book content and media solutions business in Japan. The company publishes magazines containing media, media data, and advertising media materials under the OZmagazine, metromin, AELDE, OZmall, and OzReporters brands. It also provides OZ premium reservation services, which allow online booking for hotels, restaurants, and beauty salons; and books and e-book labels, comics and digital comic labels, and film and TV adaptation rights services. In addition, the company operates websites, such as Wild Strawberries, Berry's Café, and Novema! Further, it produces internal communication and sales support tools, including brochures, posters, websites, company histories, videos, and comics. Starts Publishing Corporation was incorporated in 1983 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
